Definition: producing distorted sensory perceptions and feelings or altered states of awareness or sometimes states resembling psychosis
Example: psychedelic drugs like psilocybin and mescaline
Synonyms: noun, group, psychedelia, producing, distorted, sensory, perceptions, and, feelings, or, altered, states, of, awareness, sometimes, resembling, psychosis, drugs, like, psilocybin, mescaline
Category: adj.all
